KRUTTSCHNIT v. SIMMONS et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 23, 1903.) No. 193. Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. A. G. Bowen, for appellant. A. C. Hanff, for appellee.

Before WALLACE, LAGOMBE, and COXE, Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed, with costs, on opinion of Circuit Court. 118 Fed. 851.
